comments: Renamed 24.3.1976 to become the parish of Berkswich.

Abolished 1.4.2003 and added to the Stafford 
    unparished area and the parish of Hyde Lea.
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Stowe.
Abolished 25.3.1885 and added to the parish of Ellenhall.
Abolished 1894 and added to the parish of Stafford.

Abolished 1.4.2003 to become the parishes of Hixon and Stowe 
    by Chartley.

Abolished 1.4.1917 and divided between the parishes of Stafford 
    and Cresswell.
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Seighford.
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Marston.
